26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_ibus_gf117.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:34 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "priv.h"
30
31static int
32gf117_ibus_init(struct nvkm_subdev *ibus)
33{
34 struct nvkm_device *device = ibus->device;
35 nvkm_mask(device, 0x122310, 0x0003ffff, 0x00000800);
36 nvkm_mask(device, 0x122348, 0x0003ffff, 0x00000100);
37 nvkm_mask(device, 0x1223b0, 0x0003ffff, 0x00000fff);
38 return 0;
39}
40
41static const struct nvkm_subdev_func
42gf117_ibus = {
43 .init = gf117_ibus_init,
44 .intr = gf100_ibus_intr,
45};
46
47int
48gf117_ibus_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index,
49 struct nvkm_subdev **pibus)
50{
51 struct nvkm_subdev *ibus;
52 if (!(ibus = *pibus = kzalloc(sizeof(*ibus), GFP_KERNEL)))
53 return -ENOMEM;
54 nvkm_subdev_ctor(&gf117_ibus, device, index, 0, ibus);
55 return 0;
56}
